it.polimi.se2019.commons.utility

Interface VCEventDispatcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventDispatcher
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDeathController, CardController, Controller, DeathController, MatchController, MatchMakingController, NetworkHandler, NetworkHandlerRMI, NetworkHandlerSocket, PowerUpController, SetUpController, TurnController, WeaponController

    public interface VCEventDispatcher
extends EventDispatcher
    This class dispatches all events arriving from the view and directed to the Controller to the correct Controller that is able to handle them. See EventDispatcher.
